# Reconverse — environment variables
#
# The frontend needs NO env vars: browser calls stay same-origin (/api/v1/*) and are
# proxied to Motorverse Mission Control by api/v1/[...path].ts.
#
# Server-side only (set in the Vercel project; never committed). Optional — the proxy
# defaults to http://motorverse.genesis.lan when this is unset.
# MC_API_INTERNAL="http://motorverse.genesis.lan"
